Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest boards the old warship {\i1}Messis{\i0} and heads for the borderlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:18.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Birds in a Cage.
